{"tid":11381,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"淋早洩：我依家就係話畀大家聽，我仍然有做！","createTime":"2016-11-29T09:21:53.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-29T12:05:59.000Z","uid":6640,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"74c32e3bd8b8d6f107757f4c656126a2620ebe2b","tid":11381,"uid":6640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T09:21:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20161129&amp;guid=55981480&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20161129%26guid%3D55981480%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant&d=u%2FngHNJi%2FtIBC1CiWprX8ZkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=2320cd70\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20161129%26guid%3D55981480%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant&h=411b460e\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20161129&amp;guid=55981480&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant</a><br />\n<br />\n高登近日封殺高登第三方手機App「HKG+」，致群情洶湧，更令不少高登用戶過檔新成立「LIHKG討論區」。<br />\n<br />\n行政總裁林祖舜，就事件接受本報訪問，他表示高登流量未見受影響，每日Page view維持約600萬。對於有人於「LIHKG討論區」指他將被拉下台，連CEO都冇得做，他表示，「<span style=\"color: red;\">我依家就係話畀大家聽，我仍然有做！（屹立不倒？）暫時都屹立不倒！</span>」<br />\n<br />\n他向本報講述事件始末，他指出，當年予「HKG+」作為第三方手機App，要訂目條款，包括「HKG+」不得暫存網頁內容，以及不可自行賣廣告。不過「HKG+」早於超過半年前已被發現違反承諾，其後高登已向其作警告。至一個月前，「HKG+」再被發現私自暫存網頁內容，「你都知我哋成日收律師信，變咗有啲人以為佢係我哋，封信就畀咗我哋。因為佢地暫存我咃啲內容，我哋鏟咗就喺佢度出現返。」因此決定停止與「HKG+」合作。<br />\n<br />\n他表示，當時「HKG+」表示希望予一個月時間寬限，以對付費VIP用戶負責，「完全冇估到，原來呢個時間係籌備呢樣嘢（LIHKG）。」"},{"pid":"2d545f25f1406a87e7444b3b6006d7ab9e3168c4","tid":11381,"uid":6640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T09:22:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">做<br />\n咪攬住個殻做ceo囉</span></span>"},{"pid":"dcb87d5092a62a2cc87638c3f86edd55cace3de7","tid":11381,"uid":10035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T09:24:13.000Z","msg":"有做就好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fa37e4bc41912ffe031abbf812e0e00c4886165","tid":11381,"uid":6532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T09:24:49.000Z","msg":"做雞定做鴨"},{"pid":"6a9f1bb458b169d2633cedbaa10ef00336d91b53","tid":11381,"uid":34976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T09:25:11.000Z","msg":"暫時<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8141f9cf9a2e9bdf80cbddbcd59af3faafc0636b","tid":11381,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T09:26:14.000Z","msg":"600萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  吹到咁大<br />\n<br />\n6萬就差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"575836665d7f7b09715ab2765b5e5a63e11ec29b","tid":11381,"uid":3206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T09:26:20.000Z","msg":"自己都戴頭盔<br />\n<br />\n暫時"},{"pid":"a937095c0f8e78e06b8d64bbaee2e6b35adc0044","tid":11381,"uid":10657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T09:32:23.000Z","msg":"挑機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af1b40b2ab68f3d1420b880a88e929101934d473","tid":11381,"uid":23952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T09:32:47.000Z","msg":"自己都知暫時<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2821d0d6106fce55a69817c636c9daf4651a6f28","tid":11381,"uid":20914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T09:33:27.000Z","msg":"明修棧道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e434ed874267c37958e8e20b25c341be2461f848","tid":11381,"uid":9531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T09:35:42.000Z",